# surface-scrub denylist — copy to "surface-scrub.denylist" (gitignored) and fill in.
#
# One token per line. Blank lines and #-comments are ignored. Matching is
# case-insensitive; a hyphen-extended form (foo-cli-v2) does NOT match foo-cli,
# but an alphanumeric suffix (foo-cliv2) still flags foo-cli.
#
# List the project names, internal codenames, and domain-specific terms that must
# never appear in this toolkit's shipped skill & command examples. The real list
# stays local and untracked, so the plugin itself carries no fingerprints.

my-internal-project
internal-codename
some-domain-acronym
